to test your code. Note that this file will be used to grade your project partially since we also have our own private test cases. This is by no means an exhaustive test suite. Please feel free to add more cases to this, and test your code thoroughly. Similar to previous projects, we will test your code on a private test cases suite.
Submission Instructions
The following are requirements on your submission. Points may be deducted if they are not followed.
